# ── LootCouncil EX — gitignore ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# The repo root IS the addon: Lua / .toc / .xml are source and must be tracked.
# Ignore only machine-local state, WoW runtime data, and build artifacts.

# WoW runtime data (only relevant if the repo is cloned inside the AddOns dir)
WTF/
**/SavedVariables/
*.bak

# Packaged release archives (built artifacts, not source)
LootCouncilEX-*.zip

# Personal / machine-local Claude Code state (keep shared skills tracked).
# The negation must match the real directory case (.claude/Skills) — git pattern
# matching is case-sensitive on case-sensitive filesystems (Linux CI), even though
# core.ignorecase=true papers over it on Windows.
.claude/*
!.claude/Skills/

# Editor / IDE local settings
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
